{
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "哎呀呀，看看这是谁，生面孔啊？",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "打招呼",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_introduction",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "我只是路过而已。",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "是啊。当然。那可就稀罕了。",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_endeared",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "又路过，嗯？拿一个吧，我请客。",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_endeared",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "不过话说回来，你能坚持到现在，真有你的。\n换做别人早该放弃了。",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_endeared",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "我还有什么选择？",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "总可以一走了之。\n虽然会把涅奥气个半死，但是……",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "反驳",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/darv/darv_fear",
  "DARV.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.char": "只要这个世界还在受苦，我就不会走。",

  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "[sine]……好奇……\n……一位新的……访客……？[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "自我介绍",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_curious",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "我是来找此地的主人的。\n让他停止这场疯狂。",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "[sine]……很好……我……期待……\n……与你……共事……[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_sleepy",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]……只要 [red]他[/red] 还活着……\n……就永无宁日……[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_welcome",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.char": "又来了，又一次……\n看来我们的约定还在继续。",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.ancient": "[sine]……你会……继续战斗……\n……直到……一切终结……[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/neow/neow_sleepy",

  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "来者何人？我不记得叫过护卫啊。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "上前一步",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_eeked",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "你的守卫放我进来的。我只说了几句话。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "那想必是很有说服力的话了。\n进来吧，乌鸦。你勾起我的兴趣了。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_welcome",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "匕首、魔法、附魔的战争兵器……\n它们都有各自的用处。但你我都知道，我们最强大的武器是魅力。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_welcome",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "身为一只普通渡鸦，你的举止倒是优雅。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "不悦",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_giggle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "我当这是夸奖了。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "从我嘴里说出来？漂亮鸟儿，当然是夸奖。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_giggle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.ancient": "你确定我不能说服你效忠一位新女主人？\n涅奥浪费了你的才华，把你往墙上撞，指望墙能碎。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_giggle",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.next": "回绝",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.char": "你的馈赠我心领了。但我需要她的力量，才能夺取我为之奋斗的未来。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.ancient": "真可惜。不过如果你改主意了，这个提议一直有效。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/nonupeipe/nonupeipe_grossed_out",

  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "鸟！！傀儡鸟！为什么是傀儡？为什么是鸟！？",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "回答",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "我生来如此。",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "……而且我是我自己的主人。\n不管别人怎么说。",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-3.ancient": "哇！！说得真好！你在说谎，而我信了！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "不是傀儡的傀儡！！给你亮闪闪！鸟儿喜欢亮闪闪！",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "傀儡鸟！别打建筑师！打了没好处！",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "解释",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "一个疯王威胁着人民建立的一切。\n我怎能袖手旁观？",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "威胁不好！打仗更糟！暴力的循环！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.char": "任由靴子踩在你脸上，是逃不出这个循环的。",

  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.char": "恕我直言……你在融化。",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]是的。让你不舒服了吗……？[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "否认",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "我担心的是 [b]你[/b] 是否在意。\n更担心的是你不在意。",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-3.ancient": "[thinky_dots]为什么要在意呢？\n我沉睡着，我很满足……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]你不愿接受事物本来的样子。\n但我仍会尽力给你安慰……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]你为何如此徒劳地挣扎……？[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "告诉他",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "如果我相信自己什么都改变不了，那它就真的改变不了了。",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]如此渺小，却如此渴望重要。\n拿你想要的吧，让我安息……[/thinky_dots]",

  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient": "又是匕首！！我的失望无穷无尽！！！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "安慰",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.char": "当我的力量不足以取胜时，我便召唤巫术之力。",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient": "魔法即力量？？让我看看！！！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_curiosity",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "武器！拿一把武器！下次用剑施法！！！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "来战吧，女巫！！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "迎战",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "……！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "装死",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "已经死了！我还以为你更强呢！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.next": "说谎",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_roar",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.char": "没错。没有强力战士的协助，我毫无胜算。",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-3.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-4.ancient": "说得对！拿着这个！！！",
  "TANX.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-4.ancient.sfx": "event:/sfx/npcs/tanx/tanx_laugh",

  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.char": "至少能找到个温暖的地方，也不错。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.ancient": "哦，我只能 [jitter][b]想象[/b][/jitter] 呢。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "惊吓",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "啊。抱歉。我不是故意打扰的。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-3.ancient": "哪里的话，哪里的话！进来吧，当自己家一样。\n能迎来一位 [jitter][b]志同道合之人[/b][/jitter]，我总是很开心的。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0r.ancient": "我最近见过许多迷人的火焰，但只有一团火焰与你 [jitter][b]一样[/b][/jitter]特别。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.ancient": "别人不会说，但亲爱的，谢谢你的克制。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0.next": "询问",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.char": "什么意思？",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-2.ancient": "如果你由着性子来，早就把我们全砍倒了！\n正因你 [jitter][b]不能[/b][/jitter] 那么做，我才感激你还没试过。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.ancient": "你知道吗，母亲最大的快乐就是看着孩子们长大。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0.next": "接话",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.char": "我对你如何看待我们的关系有些顾虑。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.ancient": "[i][font_size=22]特兹卡塔拉的笑声如熔炉般隆隆作响。[/font_size][/i]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-3.ancient": "哦，亲爱的，我不是 [jitter][b]那个意思[/b][/jitter]。\n总有一天你会明白的。明白你 [sine]错过了[/sine] 什么。",

  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.char": "建筑师！这场疯狂必须停止！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-0.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.ancient": "我同意。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-1.next": "质疑",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-2.char": "不知为何，我觉得你并不真的同意。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.0-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0.ancient": "看来我是被烦人的乌鸦缠上了。真不幸，我得再杀你一次。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-0.next": "反抗",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-1.char": "死亡吓不倒我。你也一样。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-1.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-2.char": "面对邪恶，我绝不退缩。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-2.next": "开战",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-3.ancient": "试试看，鸟儿。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.1-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0r.char": "再杀死我一次！你挡不住我的！",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-1r.ancient": "可惜。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.2-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0r.ancient": "你为何坚持这场无谓的战斗？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-0r.next": "回答",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1r.char": "因为这世界可以变得更好。就算要粉身碎骨千百次，只要有一次能换来那样的未来，我也愿意。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-2r.ancient": "不会的。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.3-attack": "Both",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.4-0r.char": "如果需要的话，我会用自己的利爪把你建造的一切撕碎。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.THESORCERESSMOD-THE_SORCERESS_MOD.4-0r.next": "继续",
